{
  "description": "A vibrant hummingbird perches delicately on a slender, bare branch amidst a backdrop of golden-yellow willow leaves. The bird exhibits iridescent emerald green plumage on its body, contrasted by a striking violet-purple head and throat. Its long, slender beak points slightly upwards, as if surveying its surroundings. The willow leaves are transitioning in color, showing signs of autumn. The background is softly blurred, featuring hints of muted blue and gray, suggesting an overcast day or dappled light filtering through trees. The composition is focused on the delicate beauty of the hummingbird and the autumnal landscape.",
